<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/ayat/1> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/ayat/1/point/b> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/17/ayat/1/point/b> legal:hasKey "b" .
