<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/g> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/g> legal:hasKey "g" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/g> legal:hasText "denda dan potongan upah;" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/h> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/h> legal:hasKey "h" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/h> legal:hasText "hal-hal yang dapat diperhitungkan dengan upah;" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/i> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/i> legal:hasKey "i" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/i> legal:hasText "struktur dan  skala pengupahan yang proporsional;" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/j> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/j> legal:hasKey "j" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/j> legal:hasText "upah untuk pembayaran pesangon;  dan" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/k> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/88/ayat/3/point/k> legal:hasKey "k" .
