<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/ayat/4/point/a> legal:hasKey "a" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/ayat/4/point/a> legal:hasText "pekerja/buruh menikah, dibayar untuk selama 3 (tiga) hari;" .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/ayat/4> legal:hasPoint <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/93/ayat/4/point/b> .
