<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/ayat/3> legal:references <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101> legal:hasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/ayat/4> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/101/ayat/4> legal:hasKey 4 .
