<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/ayat/2> legal:references <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/ayat/1> .
<http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106> legal:hasAyat <http://example.org/legal/document/uu/2003/13/pasal/106/ayat/3> .
